org.simulationsystems.csf.distsys.core.api.distributedautonomousagents

Class DistributedAgentsManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.simulationsystems.csf.distsys.core.api.distributedautonomousagents.DistributedAgentsManager

  • public class DistributedAgentsManager
extends java.lang.Object
    THis manager provides some utilities for the client (e.g. CSF JADE Controller Agent) to message its own distributed autonomous agents. The client uses its own native messaging (such as FIPA ACL for JADE). Unlike the SimulationEngineManager (for the distributed system to talk to the simulation side), this class does not perform any message brokering.
    Since:
    0.1
    Version:
